{"tid":1603730,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"真係冇人拉狗，睇到眼都突埋。究竟花生友個腦係咩構造？","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:02:30.000Z","uid":205482,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8da993fc563f46c82f5117a7338e0232cf1e1f6d","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:06.000Z","msg":"(證據確鑿) 尖沙咀黑警向路過市民用警棍毆打<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/efqBrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/efqBrS</a><br />\n<br />\n[尖沙咀] 警察因言語當街打人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603290</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住啲留言話「黑警死全家」、「煲大佢」、「痴撚線」etc.<br />\n到下星期事件重演，網民又會話「納粹香港警察」、「屌黑警老母」...<br />\n到下下星期又再...<br />\n無辜市民不斷被拉，未完未了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">現正式呼籲全港市民必須調整心態，請全民勇武</div></span></span><br />\n以後再見到有無辜市民被狗拉，在場人士請勇敢少少上前<span style=\"color: orange;\">拉狗救人</span>，可唔可以？<br />\n以當時情況嚟講，街坊圍住黑警嚟屌 / 講道理嘅作用唔大，人命大過天，宜<span style=\"color: orange;\">優先救人</span><br />\n<br />\n以後除咗嗌「香港人，加油！」，唔該加多句，<span style=\"color: red;\">「香港人，覺醒！」</span>，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n小弟JJ插沙跪求各位追求進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「岳義精神，打狗救人」/「岳義精神，拉狗救人」</span></span>"},{"pid":"8893954a459cee967651430c0989dab88c0cb267","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"引用會員「HelloPePe」留言：<br />\n<blockquote>大家繼續拍片影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後大叫你地有乜權打人呀~!!!!!!!!<br />\n拎光環返屋企聽朝要返工<br />\n馬照跑舞照跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人進程</blockquote>"},{"pid":"725fc288a3178135b7b3d5fe605710fb04aa9f50","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:24.000Z","msg":"繼續引用：<br />\n<blockquote>香港人最撚叻就係等人救<br />\n要求人救<br />\n<br />\n等咩人權組織呀,快撚D文宣大核彈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等絕種啦香港人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb6226af1f3086a3f6eaf8a4c42c8194ab35e78d","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"未完<br />\n<blockquote>人權潯過左又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要惡既本土繼續惡<br />\n<br />\n印尼出到出面<br />\n香港真係欠左勇武同獅鳥<br />\n白費左佢地血同生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大核彈呀推啦爆未呀<br />\n事實係唔撚好聽,香港人就係死撚硬</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1efab8400234b5e25f6e04b3f3f5a3180274f6e7","tid":1603730,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8893954a459cee967651430c0989dab88c0cb267","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"引用會員「HelloPePe」留言：<br />\n<blockquote>大家繼續拍片影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後大叫你地有乜權打人呀~!!!!!!!!<br />\n拎光環返屋企聽朝要返工<br />\n馬照跑舞照跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人進程</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"唉，幾時先肯進化<br />\n<br />\n［手足入］希望大家可以多D留意屋企樓下E個位，提防D奇怪人搵有用垃圾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603671</a>"},{"pid":"5df5b587313177a7cbfad584be6ee7cf33eafd59","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:46.000Z","msg":"最後<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醒???不了要返工<br />\n721 831都重未識抗爭???<br />\n拍片影相,共產黨係唔會怕你<br />\n點解咁怕上面革命<br />\n<br />\n因為大家都係唔要命<br />\n死得唔夠多人足???<br />\n女手足比人姦殺又唔夠多???<br />\n你地咪拍片影相問人有咩權<br />\n重未清楚???人地就係有權姦你殺你<br />\n明未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9739bd4ee560414ea46ae43889684d78fe3d0963","tid":1603730,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"即場問有冇人跟隊打波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3441ad2263ffe64bb48482cdd1157fcfbf20bbf2","tid":1603730,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">岳義精神 打狗救人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf77c799e8c23c5ab645e159ce0a5c7ce0a2e831","tid":1603730,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"建議出本說明書<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔睇說明書圖文並茂係學唔識"},{"pid":"774e9597521b7f199e0394852375c4df965e8f65","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"現正式呼籲全港市民必須調整心態，請全民勇武"},{"pid":"3b93854ef04e8cb1a657636bfdbf3576ee105aaf","tid":1603730,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"現正式呼籲全港市民必須調整心態，請全民勇武"},{"pid":"46108faadbe4b61912d4ef6387f18fb38b441e64","tid":160